{"tid":2288693,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"在中國出生的哈薩克人，卻面臨被迫離婚、放棄護照的荒唐夢魘","createTime":"2020-11-16T16:09:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-16T18:12:48.000Z","uid":261647,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e45bd2f1565cd32d80d6e939620ec37c4adfdac6","tid":2288693,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T16:09:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/TheNewsLens/posts/3454267804642684\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FTheNewsLens%2Fposts%2F3454267804642684&d=Mbax9TUBBsNKvtRo7%2B5fu4RM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=95329da1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/TheNewsLens/posts/3454267804642684</a><br />\n<br />\n【在中國出生的哈薩克人，卻面臨被迫離婚、放棄護照的荒唐夢魘】<br />\n<br />\n和許多在中國出生的哈薩克人一樣，澤米斯古爾的父母埃爾博拉特和烏米森在蘇聯解體後，接受哈薩克政府的召喚，回到了他們「歷史的家鄉」，成了哈薩克公民。<br />\n<br />\n但是，一次再平常不過的中國行，卻成了一家子醒不過來的夢魘：新疆地方在他們入境後沒收了他們的哈薩克護照，理由是他們利用中國1997年配給他們的土地賺取收益，必須賠償。<br />\n<br />\n當地警察更告訴烏米森，她們的婚姻會「傷害」埃爾博拉特，最好還是離婚。「等等，為什麼要逼他們離婚？」幫我做論文最後校訂的老公茫然地問我&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tVoUocC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtVoUocC.png&h=c3b0cdb9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e446f2d85dacd30e335a9cd0abfb93c762d9979b","tid":2288693,"uid":293012,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T16:40:33.000Z","msg":"咁同綁架外國人有乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d12ea77eca3efdc4850e899d02c50c7409cd2738","tid":2288693,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T17:30:25.000Z","msg":"共匪=恐怖份子<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" clas